Scott A. Cameron (sacame@cc.umanitoba.ca) wrote:
: Looking at plain text versus cypher text in a statistical sense
: i've discovered i can't.

: Where do I find work done on word distributions and analysis on
: how the words are most/least commonly formed in the english 
: language. 

: Yes I realize that I could collect a huge text library of common
: english and statistically analyze it myself. It just seems like
: doing work that's been done before is wasteful.  Not to mention
