My Moby Words product has several frequency lists and the raw
material to make your own as well; the Brown Corpus is available
but is a little aged since the sixties.

Some of the more expensive crypto books published by the Aegean Press
have trigrams for certain universes of messages.

If you have a specific question, I'll be glad to post what I can find
to this group...


